Specify the input sample format. It is set by default to \f(CW\*(C`none\*(C'\fR.
.IP "\fBosf, out_sample_fmt\fR" 4
.IX Item "osf, out_sample_fmt"
Specify the output sample format. It is set by default to \f(CW\*(C`none\*(C'\fR.
