.IX Item "dplii"
select Dolby Pro Logic \s-1II\s0
.RE
.RS 4
.Sp
Default value is \f(CW\*(C`none\*(C'\fR.
.RE
.IP "\fBfilter_type\fR" 4
.IX Item "filter_type"
For swr only, select resampling filter type. This only affects resampling
